title: Dynasties, Jerry Jones, Urban Meyer, and the NFL playoffs
itunes:title: Dynasties, Jerry Jones, Urban Meyer, and the NFL playoffs
description:
Colin talks about the curtain dynasties in sports that are close to dying, why Dallas Cowboys owner Jerry Jones waited so long to fire Jason Garrett, why he probably wont hire Urban Meyer, and his NFL Wild Card picks for the weekend. Guests include Albert Breer, Peter King, Eric Dickerson, Daryl Johnston, and Jason McIntyre.
